						<p>California Institute of Integral Studies (CIIS)</p>
						<p><strong>MFA in Theatre</strong></p>
					</div>

					<div class="credential">
						<h3>Specialized Certifications</h3>
						<p><strong>Certified Brainspotting Therapist</strong></p>
						<p>Advanced Brainspotting training (Phases 1 & 2)</p>
						<p><strong>Expansion Brainspotting</strong> for performance</p>
					</div>

					<div class="credential">
						<h3>Additional Training</h3>
						<p><strong>Certified Grief Recovery Specialist</strong></p>
						<p>The Grief Recovery Method</p>
						<p><strong>Play Therapy Training</strong></p>
						<p><strong>Fertility Psychological Evaluations</strong></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section section-light">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Serving the Oakland Community</h2>

				<div class="content-flow">
					<p>
						My practice is based in Oakland at 3637 Grand Ave, and I serve clients throughout the Bay Area—including Berkeley, Alameda, Piedmont, and beyond.
					</p>

					<p>
						I offer both in-person sessions at my Oakland office and secure telehealth sessions for those who prefer online therapy or live outside the immediate area.
					</p>

					<p>
						Whether you're dealing with trauma, grief, anxiety, infertility, or creative blocks—or you're simply seeking deeper healing and self-understanding—I'm here to support you.
					</p>

					<p>
						For more information about my practice, services, and approach, visit my main website at <a href="https://megangredesky.com">MeganGredesky.com</a>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section section-cta">
			<div class="container cta-content">
				<h2>Ready to Begin Your Healing Journey?</h2>
				<p class="lead">Schedule your free 15-minute consultation to see if we're a good fit and learn how Brainspotting can support your healing.</p>

				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<ConsultationButton variant="primary" size="large" location="about_cta" />
				</div>

				<p class="cta-note">Serving Oakland, Berkeley, Alameda, and throughout the Bay Area • In-person and telehealth available</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

